.max-w-prose
  = doc_info(url: "https://github.com/profoundry-us/loco_motion/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md", icon: "arrow-up-circle", icon_css: "text-primary") do
    :markdown
      Until _Loco_**Motion** reaches 1.0.0, **every minor release should be
